<body>
    <%- include("../views/includes/header") -%>
<main>
    <div class="container py-5">
        <!-- Central Container for About Us Section -->
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <img class="card-img" src="./Images/Adsett Seating.webp" alt="Library photo">
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card custom-border-card" style="min-height: 400px;"> 
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column"> 
                        <h1 class="card-title">About Us:</h1>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            AML is a national network of library branches spread across all cities and towns in England, providing a wide range of media services, including books, journals, periodicals, CDs, DVDs, games, and multimedia titles.
                            AML operates under a central governance structure with its headquarters located in London, overseeing budget management and overall strategy. Each city or town has a main branch, with larger cities like Sheffield and Manchester having multiple branches to meet demand, while smaller towns may operate with just one. Resources such as books and media are shared among branches and managed by the primary branch to ensure efficient utilization.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <!-- Image Section -->
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <img class="card-img" src="./Images/Adsett Library.webp" alt="Library photo">
            </div>
        
            <!-- Catalogue Card Section -->
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <div class="card custom-border-card" style="min-height: 400px;"> 
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column"> 
                        <h1 class="card-title">Catalogue:</h1>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            This is where you can find our catalogue with a wide range of different media, including books, journals, periodicals, CDs, DVDs, games, and multimedia titles.
                        </p>
                        <a href="catalogue.html" class="btn btn-custom mt-auto">Browse Catalogue</a> 
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="row mb-4">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="card custom-border-card">
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <h1 class="card-title">News Feed:</h1>
                        <p class="card-text">
                            Stay updated with our latest stock and library news.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</main>
